app_description: Prodrafts the last pieces of paperless learning. It is an endless draft with a scale of 600x and the algorithm is optimized so that it can draw vertically with a swipe of the pen. It is another window of learning software with all kinds of notes software to follow the flow of ideas It is also a manager for integrating all kinds of files free interception demo sharing is not a problem. So whether it s studying or working it fits seamlessly into your process. Just as PDF note taking software helps you lose your book Prodrafts help you drop that draft book.
